{"tid":397194,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企同時有養貓狗？","createTime":"2017-09-12T09:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T14:14:07.000Z","uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5258c5247046dc16e44b854f0d0098e491aca92b","tid":397194,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T09:53:47.000Z","msg":"佢地平時係屋企會唔會同大家玩下定係唔理大家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會唔會怕佢地會打交？<br />\n<br />\n利伸屋企有隻柴犬有dd惡，想養多隻貓但怕番到去會恰隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a26b35e94848f012919ef1fc2cba6f8d761a30b","tid":397194,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T09:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28394d6ab3787faea66fbd845bc094416d18fe6a","tid":397194,"uid":12526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:05:58.000Z","msg":"隻狗10歲 貓3歲<br />\n隻狗比隻貓恰<br />\n平時好少會兩個痴埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5a5a99a037e1e5babdce236f03ff2be022704b","tid":397194,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:12:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻狗10歲 貓3歲<br />\n隻狗比隻貓恰<br />\n平時好少會兩個痴埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地會唔會一齊玩？ 定實情其實唔理大家？<br />\n<br />\n我隻狗對住其他狗一係就惡人一係就唔理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9949aa389472147522d01b7319e07e8fb4dbd286","tid":397194,"uid":54728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隻狗10歲 貓3歲<br />\n隻狗比隻貓恰<br />\n平時好少會兩個痴埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地會唔會一齊玩？ 定實情其實唔理大家？<br />\n<br />\n我隻狗對住其他狗一係就惡人一係就唔理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我隻狗成日都做主動想同貓玩，但係隻貓唔領情一下就拍開佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54b78f47ed9ad270bdad403f9ea0903fc775982","tid":397194,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:40:42.000Z","msg":"狗係唔夠貓打"},{"pid":"1a35acb56cf3941d15785a68c1c6209c160a57d9","tid":397194,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:32:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f393650aa5a6b93e70da421be6785140fc574cf","tid":397194,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"無養貓冇知一問佢係咪會周屋跳？<br />\n<br />\n姐係會隨時跳上枱面，跳上床之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可唔可以教識佢唔好跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027c935996efd8c82c1cb10cd87018e76cbf2eee","tid":397194,"uid":51726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無養貓冇知一問佢係咪會周屋跳？<br />\n<br />\n姐係會隨時跳上枱面，跳上床之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可唔可以教識佢唔好跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓冇狗對人類果種服從性<br />\n唔好期望會教得到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853ad84ed6ecd0df570c9c85e261656626c2de72","tid":397194,"uid":125646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無養貓冇知一問佢係咪會周屋跳？<br />\n<br />\n姐係會隨時跳上枱面，跳上床之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可唔可以教識佢唔好跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我屋企隻貓成日跳上跳落，教唔掂"},{"pid":"3eb052b67689ed850c5f240172f62ab1f5d62617","tid":397194,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"試過一狗兩貓同一貓一狗，而家一狗一貓（但唔係之前嗰對<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。以前嗰對好friend架隻貓會幫狗lam毛又會一齊瞓一齊玩，而家呢對都一齊玩，但玩得好暴力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c04baba8c1ce2ae154321d88f496b7d1bc6962b","tid":397194,"uid":7022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"隻狗8歲 隻貓3個月 <br />\n一開頭隻狗會有啲激動 但過幾日慣左陣味就無野<br />\n隻貓會撩佢玩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632ba37b085fcaf51065c14cbcb4f4591d47e683","tid":397194,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻狗10歲 貓3歲<br />\n隻狗比隻貓恰<br />\n平時好少會兩個痴埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d0b1c858629f1f1d4068176850c67602579ee59e","tid":397194,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]隻狗10歲 貓3歲<br />\n隻狗比隻貓恰<br />\n平時好少會兩個痴埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[啱/quote]</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱啱我隻雀亂篤mon㩒錯製"},{"pid":"2d0533c3c6438f25930facfe2cee140106fdda44","tid":397194,"uid":42407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:43:08.000Z","msg":"在野黨主席兼職總冠軍獎盃是"},{"pid":"71526635822bdb7cf2830bdda23d99c8d798ba99","tid":397194,"uid":12526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:32:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隻狗10歲 貓3歲<br />\n隻狗比隻貓恰<br />\n平時好少會兩個痴埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地會唔會一齊玩？ 定實情其實唔理大家？<br />\n<br />\n我隻狗對住其他狗一係就惡人一係就唔理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貓無狗咁好接受力<br />\n所以養貓嘅話最好由bb仔開始養<br />\n趁佢認知未成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc73d0cc8fce0bc4bd34dbe0d203a29d53f4a72e","tid":397194,"uid":21638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/134316_3f9bb6b7bdabcecf6fdc003ca03b65bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F134316_3f9bb6b7bdabcecf6fdc003ca03b65bb.jpg&h=649afc83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我隻貓淨係會同依隻狗玩<br />\n屋企有三隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a781d02dd5c19607b0f663bc192b7ebaa62775e0","tid":397194,"uid":21638,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/134316_3f9bb6b7bdabcecf6fdc003ca03b65bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F134316_3f9bb6b7bdabcecf6fdc003ca03b65bb.jpg&h=649afc83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我隻貓淨係會同依隻狗玩<br />\n屋企有三隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過其實我本身麻麻地養貓<br />\n隻貓係佢三日大時係工作地方比貓媽遺棄<br />\n執左返屋企又行過鬼門關一轉<br />\n<br />\n我隻唐狗就貓痴黎既，勁中意貓<br />\n所以諗住拎隻貓返黎比佢開心下<br />\n<br />\n我隻唐狗最中意狂反轉隻貓...隻貓又好enjoy<br />\n幫朋友暫養狗時佢地想同貓玩...<br />\n隻貓會發脾氣樹起晒d毛，係依隻唔會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/134727_f75052fcae165b83dcb472975810fde4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F134727_f75052fcae165b83dcb472975810fde4.jpg&h=e8aaada7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隻貓睇獸醫時係人都抱得<br />\n個個抱親都會煲水同奶奶手<br />\n獸醫話一千隻都冇一隻係咁既性格<br />\n一返屋企都冇掂佢佢就狂煲水<br />\n要lur人抱<br />\n又唔驚剪指甲<br />\n<br />\n本身帶佢返黎時想試下可唔可以訓練做一隻狗<br />\n依家好似貓狗mix做一隻野咁...玩唔停唔中意訓覺<br />\n又百厭...有時想佢好似其他貓咁狂訓..."},{"pid":"18cc0355b3088a4460bd9008a2d6c29420a990a9","tid":397194,"uid":31998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/135539_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F135539_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=71c522c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝早同夜晚會追逐一輪。玩到攰就各自訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd49a5f3cfb3b09717eef581fcb246d348fa434","tid":397194,"uid":82362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:14:07.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}